Torchmark Corp said its boardauthorized the purchase from time to time of a significantportion of its 7-3/4 pct convertible subordinated debentures.As of February 25, it said there were outstanding 150 mln dlrsof the principal amount of debenures.    The company also said it plans to redeem the debentures onJune eight.    It also declared a regular quarterly dividend of 25 cts pershare on its common payable May one to shareholders of recordApril 10. Reuter&#3;